&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Part of a larger toolkit&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a href="https://github.com/yurukusa/claude-code-ops-starter" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;claude-code-ops-starter&lt;/a&gt; ‚Äî 4 free safety hooks + the generator + a CLAUDE.md template&lt;/li&gt;
